n$91.300\n2572,020 $1 72.325 0 553,940\n47,002 r.150 $17,\u00a37.11 2*\nI\nThe Miner regrets being unable to publish full and accurate returns\nWe have made repeated effort* to obtain the necessary Information from\nthe mine manager*. Such return* a* are ettituated or are lacking from\nthe above tabic we will nultllsh a* soon a* we receive them.\n1884\nCoeur d'Alene Mines\n1907\n\nLots\nChoice Home Sites, only six miles from Wallace,\nfronting on the county road and right of way of the\nSpokane, Wallace Interstate electric railway, all level\nwith good soil and drainage, smallest lots 50x100 with wide streets and\nalleys.\nGood Water System Splendid Fire Protection\nThe property consists of part of the Evolution ranch and adjoins the\nEvolution and Legal Tender mines. It is held by patent from the United\nStates.\nPrices from $100 to $300\nTerms: $10 Down and $10 a Month\nNEW CHICAGO MINING CO\n\nCapital $1,500,000 with 750,000 Shares in Treasury. This group of mines on the\nNorth Fork is under development and will begin shipping as soon as the Idaho Northern\nrailway, now under construction, is ready for business. I have a small block of treasury shares\nfor sale at 10c a Share, payable one cent a share down and the balance in nine equal monthly\npayments.\nOther Buys I Recommend\nWest Nine Mile, 5c\nLegal Tender, 15c\nArctic Mining Milling Co., 3c\nCoeur d'Alene Carbonate, 5c\nThe above are all treasury stocks\nSilver Moon, 5c\nShoshone 15c\nPhone 159 K\nP. 0. Box 126\nWallace,\n412\nIdaho\nSixth St.\nA Good Thing\nIs never certain.\nThe only exception\nwe know is Montana-Mammoth, a mine\nwith a 42-foot vein and a thousand tons\nof shipping ore On the dump.\nThe C L MITCHELL CO.\n300428 Columbia Building\nSPOKANE. WASH.\nStock\nCertificates\nWe have them. The larg\nest and most complete\nline in the Coeur d'Alenes.\nComplete outfits for\ncompanies furnished at\nthe shortest notice.\nnew\nMiner Job\nOffice\nPhone 174\nWALLACE\n719 Bank St.","height":"21216","width"